725636f-a.title: Queens: 74th Street - 34th Avenue
725636f-a.text:
74th Street, north from and across 34th Avenue, showing the thoroughfares and new apartment houses being constructed on forner farmland along the west side of the old Trains
Meadow Road.
P. L. Sperr  October 21, 1936

725637f-a.title: Queens: 74th Street - 34th Avenue
725637f-a.text:
76th Street, east side, between 35th and 34th Avenues, showing an old cottage, which was either the J. Johnson or Bartley property in 1873. It was then on Trains Meadow Road,
hnow no longer in existence.
P. L. Sperr  October 21, 1936
